title: Help please!
body: When I click to launch LoL it does not work? This is the first time this has happened to me after the recent patch. I have tried to run as administrator however it still does not work. Any ideas? :(

replies.body:
Hi,

Can you elaborate a little on what does not work?  Does the launcher show up?  Are you able to login?

One potential cause is that we did hear of some potential ISP issues last night for some players, but they should be resolved now.  What ISP are you with?

Cheers
Mindstar
